branchCategory.name: SFD, Clean Air Filter
branchCategory.description: <P>SF series clean air filters are available as cartridge type or disposable type models.  The filtration level is 0.01 micron (filtering efficiency of 99.99%) on units with membrane elements.  The SFB20, with a sintered metallic element, has a nominal filtration of 120 micron.  The SF series can be used under different environments with chemical resistant and heat resistant materials (refer to catalog specifications for each series).</P>
